---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHero from "../../components/PageHero";
import silenceImg from "../../assets/images/silence.webp";
import deepakImg from "../../assets/images/team/deepak-profile.webp";

const article = {
    title: "The Rebellion of Silence",
    subtitle: "Philosophy of Marga",
    heroImage: silenceImg.src,
    date: "January 15, 2026",
    author: "Deepak Mahato Tharu",
    readTime: "6 min read",
};
---

<Layout
    title={article.title}
    description="In a noisy world, silence is rebellion. Learn how Marga Adventure integrates mindfulness and silence into high-altitude trekking."
    image={article.heroImage}
>
    <PageHero
        title="Silence"
        subtitle="The loudest sound in the world."
        image={article.heroImage}
        parallax={true}
    />

    <article class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            {/* Header Info */}
            <div
                class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-100 pb-8 mb-12"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gray-100 overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <img
                            src={deepakImg.src}
                            alt="Deepak"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p
                            class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900"
                        >
                            {article.author}
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
                        >
                            CIO & Strategist
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-900">
                        {article.date}
                    </p>
                    <p
                        class="text-[10px] text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
                    >
                        {article.readTime}
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Content */}
            <div
                class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-serif prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:text-gray-900 prose-p:text-gray-800 prose-blockquote:font-serif prose-blockquote:text-brand-dark prose-blockquote:not-italic prose-blockquote:border-brand max-w-none leading-loose"
            >
                <p
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-serif italic mb-10 leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-brand pl-8 py-2"
                >
                    "We live in an age of notification. The ping, the buzz, the
                    red dot. To choose silence in a world screaming for your
                    attention is the ultimate act of rebellion."
                </p>

                <p class="mb-8">
                    When was the last time you heard absolutely nothing? No
                    distant hum of traffic, no whir of a server room, no
                    playlist filling the void. Just... nothing. Or perhaps, just
                    the terrifyingly loud sound of your own heartbeat, or the
                    crunch of snow under a boot at 4,000 meters?
                </p>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    At Marga Adventure, we believe that in the 21st century, the
                    greatest luxury is not gold taps or 500-thread-count sheets. <strong
                        >The ultimate luxury is undistracted attention.</strong
                    > It is the ability to be fully here, now.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
                    The Digital Detox
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    As a technologist, I see the toll. We are wired but
                    disconnected. We curate our lives for an audience we don't
                    know, missing the life happening right in front of us. We
                    curate our trips to break this cycle. We take you to the
                    shadow of the Annapurnas, where the signal bars fade to
                    zero.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    Panic sets in for the first hour. The phantom vibration in
                    your pocket. The itch to check email. Boredom sets in for
                    the second. You don't know where to look.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    And then, something magical almost spiritual happens. The
                    boredom gives way to observation. You notice the way the
                    light turns the snow gold at sunset. You notice the
                    intricate carving on a Mani stone. You notice that the knot
                    in your chest has loosened. You are free.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="my-16 bg-brand/5 p-10 rounded-3xl border border-brand/10 relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 text-brand/10"
                    >
                        <svg
                            width="100"
                            height="100"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="currentColor"
                        >
                            <path
                                d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-1-13h2v6h-2zm0 8h2v2h-2z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-xl mb-4 font-serif">
                        The Gift of Stillness
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        We don't impose silence, we invite it. On our journeys,
                        you'll find moments where the only playlist is the wind
                        through the pines and the distant roar of a glacial
                        river. We create spaces like quiet sunrises or fireside
                        evenings where you can disconnect from the network and
                        reconnect with your own thoughts. It's in these
                        uncurated moments that the true journey begins.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
                    Returning Home
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    Our goal is not just to give you a break, but to give you a
                    tool. When you return to the cacophony of the city, you
                    carry a piece of the Himalayan silence within you. You
                    realize that you can access that "Marga" state anywhere. You
                    realize you don't have to answer every ping.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Silence isn't empty. It's full of the answers you've been
                    too busy to hear.
                </p>
            </div>

            {/* Footer Nav */}
            <div
                class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-gray-100 flex justify-between items-center"
            >
                <a
                    href="/blog/the-origin-story"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
                    >← Previous</a
                >
                <a
                    href="/blog/beyond-tourism"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
                    >Next Story →</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</Layout>
